          "type": "text",
          "id": "LqkTQ",
          "name": "specBody",
          "fill": "#495057",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 5600,
          "content": "Atomic template tier (atoms → molecules → AuthLayout). WCAG 2.1 AA: sufficient contrast, 40px+ controls, keyboard-friendly grouping. RTL: logical flex layout and symmetric padding—verify mirrored in DirectionProvider. Spacing rhythm 24–32px. Global token example --av-color-primary: #228BE6; brand/tenant overrides via tier-2 tokens without rebuild.",
          "lineHeight": 1.45,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    }
